<div tiddler="NestedTemplates" modifier="JeremyRuston" modified="200609291536" created="200609291536" tags="features">A PageTemplate, ViewTemplate or EditTemplate can include the text of another tiddler by including it in double square brackets. For example:\n\n{{{\n&lt;div&gt;\n[[MyHeader]]\n&lt;/div&gt;\n}}}\n\nYou can also use TiddlerSlicing format to include a smaller chunk of the text of a tiddler.</div>